**<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif; font-size: 12pt;">The desire to overcome American alienation the international sphere is merely an attempt to repress the specter of Vietnam which haunts post-Iraq United States by ameliorating the anxiety produced by the visible violence of an imperial state</span>**
